    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Coffee culture has rapidly grown in modern China, especially in urban areas. 咖啡店 (coffee shops)\nhave become popular social gathering places, and the term 咖啡 represents not just the beverage but\nalso Western café culture and lifestyle. The coffee brown color (咖啡色) is also commonly used in\nfashion and design contexts."}],"type":"paragraph"}
